      • registerDecorator

        public void registerDecorator(@Nonnull
                              MessageDecorator<?> decorator)
        Register a decorator in this module. If you want your decorator to be serialized and restored after a shutdown, you need to register it.

        Can also be performed by MessageDecorator.register(MessageDecoratorModule).

        Parameters:
        decorator - The decorator to register.
        See Also:
        MessageDecorator.register(MessageDecoratorModule), MessageDecorator.register(ModularBot)

        Parameters:
